      <p>I actually saw this sauce on the lunch menu the other day at craftbar in nyc and ordered after reading this post. It was served with a battered skate fillet and fingerling potatoes. Might I say that this chopped egg, olive oil, and caper flavored sauce was light and refreshing against the buttery starchiness of the roasted fingerlings. Yum!</p>
